Iyobosa Rehoboth, nke a makwaara dị ka Prodigeezy, bụ onye nduzi vidio egwu na onye na-ese ihe nkiri na Naijiria.
Rehoboth si Edo Steeti na Naịjirịa
O tolitere na Port Harcourt, Nigeria.

Prodigeezy eduziela ọtụtụ vidiyo egwu maka ndị na-edekọ egwu n'ụdị dị iche iche, nke gụnyere egwu nke Falz wetara esemokwu a kpọrọ "This Is Nigeria", Killin' Dem nke Burna Boy, Don't Call me back nke Joeboy, Joey B, Falz, Ric Hassani, tinyere ndị ọzọ.
N'afọ 2018, o meriri Best Music Video of the Year (Director) site na Nigeria Entertainment Awards maka ọrụ ya This Is Nigeria
N'afọ 2019, The Headies họpụtara ya maka Best Music Video of the Year (Director) maka ọrụ ya "Talk".
